## Interrupt & Control

| Shortcut | Action |
|----------|--------|
| `Esc` | Stop generation mid-response |
| `Esc` + `Esc` | Rewind to previous state |
| `Ctrl+C` | Cancel current input/generation |
| `Ctrl+D` | Exit Claude Code session |

## Screen & History

| Shortcut | Action |
|----------|--------|
| `Ctrl+L` | Clear terminal screen (keeps conversation) |
| `Ctrl+R` | Reverse search command history |
| `Up/Down` | Navigate through previous inputs |
| `Ctrl+O` | Toggle verbose output |
| `?` | Show available shortcuts |

## Mode Switching

| Shortcut | Action |
|----------|--------|
| `Shift+Tab` | Cycle: Normal -> Auto-Accept -> Plan Mode |
| `Option+P` (Mac) / `Alt+P` | Switch model mid-prompt |

## Input Methods

### Images

- `Ctrl+V` - Paste image from clipboard (NOT Cmd+V on Mac)

### Multiline Input

| Method | How |
|--------|-----|
| Quick escape | `\` + `Enter` |
| macOS default | `Option+Enter` |
| After setup | `Shift+Enter` (run `/terminal-setup` first) |

## Quick Prefixes

| Prefix | Name | Action |
|--------|------|--------|
| `/` | Slash command | Execute built-in or custom command |
| `#` | Memory | Add instruction to CLAUDE.md |
| `!` | Bash | Run shell command directly |
| `@` | File mention | Trigger file path autocomplete |

