## Background Execution

Run long commands without blocking:

- Ask Claude to run in background, OR
- Press `Ctrl+B` to background current bash command
- Use `/bashes` to manage background tasks

## Custom Commands

Create reusable workflows:

- Project commands: `.claude/commands/*.md`
- Personal commands: `~/.claude/commands/*.md`

Execute with `/project:command-name` or `/user:command-name`.

Supports `$ARGUMENTS`, `$1`, `$2` for arguments. See Tip #30 for details.
